passages.name: 0N1
passages.text: {Oh, you look nice all dressed up, what is the special occasion young man?} <%= links['503d333ad613286c61b75f997d0d88c83e225e05'] %> <%= links['6d663166ae201f2ffab88029683f873a2ae3662b'] %>

passages.name: 1P1
passages.text: {This is just my work attire, I work at an accounting firm.} <%= links['2b3210f0e163fb28b0e60d2985acd5f59a8e9a4b'] %>

passages.name: 1P2
passages.text: {This is just the way that I dress!} <%= links['5ccb490d122dface3f7adc04825671cb23a5d75a'] %>

passages.name: 2N1
passages.text: {Oh what an important job, do you enjoy it there?} <%= links['ec23157ccb0b8e7f2d15a6dd43c07115668793d5'] %> <%= links['e9f2d93f939667fb8655f829688be22ac1d56f07'] %>

passages.name: 2N2X
passages.text: {Oh I see, well it looks good on you!}

passages.name: 3P1
passages.text: {Not really, I'm trying to find some other joys in life because of that} <%= links['c0c2885b2867914774d791b63ef700c6cfae9a28'] %>

passages.name: 3P2
passages.text: {Being an accountant is what I was born to do, but I also find many other joys in my life.} <%= links['105cefd1d3e197cbd3cea5b6a9841028016ecaae'] %>

passages.name: 4N1X
passages.text: {I hope you find what you are looking for then!}

passages.name: 4N2X
passages.text: {I'm glad you like what you do sweety!}
